{
  "stem": "1828.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And save as many people as we can as they were coming in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had maps, and they risked their lives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They made it to freedom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The partisans picked them up, and we know from after the war that these maps were delivered and never acted upon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The railroad tracks were never bombed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we were on our way out of Auschwitz, and after some hours, maybe it was a day, somebody crawled up to look out that little window and said, we must be in Germany.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It-- the signs say it's Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they lifted me up on their shoulders, and I looked out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yes it is German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was totally bilingual.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I understood what it was saying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was totally overwhelmed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Suddenly you see green lawns and flowers, and it must have been Sunday, because people were going to church, obviously in their finery.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And flowers growing, and-- and-- and life going on while we were buried alive there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It-- it just brought it back to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You see, and-- while you are in-- in-- in such a situation, not that anyone can imagine what it's like, you make nice little compartments out of the day in order to survive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You say this hour, that hour, we eat now, and it's going to be fine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you say just if I get through this long walk in my shoes, the-- the-- the wooden shoes, I'll be fine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So you don't look at a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You look at an hour.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You look at a small package of time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this really shocked us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We took turns looking out that window and seeing normal life, manicured lawns, people sitting at a picnic table, or whatever it was there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and this didn't seem right.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
